Package: IdfHydroPckg
Type: Package
Title: Hydrological Package for IDF (Intensity-Duration-Frequency) Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mohsen Amirian
Maintainer: xamim003@studenti.czu.cz
Description: 
    IdfHydroPckg is an R package designed for conducting Intensity-Duration-Frequency (IDF) analysis in hydrology. 
    It provides functions for importing NetCDF files, calculating IDF models, and visualizing IDF curves.
    The package is intended to assist hydrologists, researchers, and engineers in analyzing extreme precipitation events 
    and understanding their frequency and intensity patterns.
    Use four spaces when indenting paragraphs within the Description.
